text: Miloslav Bělonožník (11 July 1918 - 12 January 2010) was a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Vysoké nad Jizerou
